 Galvatron lands at the coordinates. He transformed into his drill mode and 
burrowed under ground to await the bots arrival. The deep earth would keep 
him from being detected. His back legs kicked the dirt back as he drilled 
covering his way in keeping any type of folllowing or shots at him through 
his tunel. His masquito bot satyed behind and waited for the bots arrival.
